od gave him 10 times of what he had, family, fortune, and so forth, but did all that replace what God had taken from him?  That was my turning point in my belief in Christianity, the ideals are good if you get past all the bull shit, but we humans are too self involved and chaotic to do so.  Therefore in my humble opinion we will use our religions our faith and what ever else you wish to call it, to control, to rule over others and get the since of I am the alpha dog in this little world.  We can not help ourselves.<br>
<br>
